# API Services

- Build URLs with `environment.*` and `appUrls.*`; avoid inline endpoint strings.
- Use shared wrappers from `src/app/config/api-config/callMethods.tsx`; avoid raw `axios` in services.
- Export small named service functions; keep one responsibility per function.
- Avoid `any` in request or response signatures; prefer typed DTOs and interfaces.
- Keep query-string building centralized (`getQueryParams`) instead of string concatenation.
- Keep auth and refresh behavior in shared API config; do not duplicate token logic in each service.
